##Create new list to extract the hour and minutes information from Timestamp field
hours=[]
for i in combine_df['Date']:
    t=i.to_pydatetime()
    hours.append(t.hour)
minutes=[]
for i in combine_df['Date']:
    t=i.to_pydatetime()
    minutes.append(t.minute)
    
    
combine_df['Minute']=minutes
combine_df['Hour']=hours
